{"tid":1670311,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我正式宣布 邊個再開加泰Po 邊個係鬼","createTime":"2019-10-23T03:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T04:17:49.000Z","uid":116910,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"27c9efedafb3df70ec73d760ac212221beb0d8bd","tid":1670311,"uid":116910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:06:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母一起身熱門五個Po講加泰<br />\n三個Po話去 兩個屌人唔好去<br />\n<br />\n我咩立場都唔撚比<br />\n跟自己初心<br />\n你了解完加泰既歷史 近況 支持就去<br />\n乜都唔明 唔想了解 就咪撚去<br />\n<br />\n就係咁簡單 <br />\n人地話去就去咁同撐警大盟有乜柒分別？ <br />\n陣間去到比記者問 你究竟支持 加泰獨立<br />\n反暴 反黑警 都未搞清楚 <br />\n發生咩事又唔知 國際立場又唔知 <br />\n<br />\n當太多聲音同分化Po就諗翻我地初心先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> <br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"df92e8bdfaac0f01628dfbb42f9ae038f2b4692e","tid":1670311,"uid":223296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:07:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb78e95c087bc4bdc39b584a585c870cbe182e5f","tid":1670311,"uid":182827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:15:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqKDBGo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqKDBGo.jpg&h=5178288a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4f3NN3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa4f3NN3.jpg&h=682a02d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b68a9f6f55a443960ecf1d47b8aa8a01f4033a7","tid":1670311,"uid":116910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:15:33.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"0cea0ab805c77c85419e8632bf0b2507ea0ade42","tid":1670311,"uid":221360,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:15:43.000Z","msg":"去集會果班，唔代表全香港，就好似撐警集會咁，都唔係代表全香港。想去就去，唔想去咪唔好去，反而覺得大家post多d點解要支持／反對個集會既post，比大家自行決定會更加好。<br />\n最後，集會無可能影響我地既初衷，去既只係聲援佢地為自由所做既事，